Dear friends, 
we’re very excited to announce that from today on you can use your lovely Calculator Air app in dark and light mode. 
Now you can protect your eyes from bright light and save your battery life.

PS: Please do not forget to leave us your comments.

- Your Calculator team

Our greatest update ever!

SNAP AND SOLVE
Take a photo of an equation and we will provide you the solution! In seconds you will get an answer, a graph and even guidance on how to solve it!

HISTORY
Browse through all of your calculations and find the result you were looking for!

FAVORITES
Save your recurrent or important calculations.
